    "motivation": "This governance action mandates the introduction of a secp256r1 builtin to Cardano's Plutus VM, on a reasonable implementation schedule.\n\n *Not to be confused with secp256k1, which Cardano already supports.*\n Secp256r1 support is valuable because of its availability in a wide range of secure hardware technology. Key example: it is the curve used in the Secure Enclave on iPhones and across the Apple ecosystem. With this primitive, Cardano developers would be able to deploy mobile wallets with stronger security than possible today.",
